 -The Brobecks, If You Like It Or Not

If there's one thing you don't want to do, it's to lie to the sapient and very capable AI about the nature of its arrangement with you and then not expect it to get pissed off.

Thanks to Popsioak, and everybody else who looked over this for crit, and to whoever gave me these conprocs. Seriously, thank you for helping me to come up with this thing. I could not have done it without any of the aforementioned people, and I hope that you enjoyed this piece.





